{"tid":2157801,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★返工=?? 葵涌貨櫃碼頭 宏記港務料百員工需送檢疫中心","createTime":"2020-08-15T09:31:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T18:09:07.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a13cbe9c81764a49b7f8e140f95068a49177e7d5","tid":2157801,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T09:31:01.000Z","msg":"群組方面，有27宗與之前個案有相關，當中22宗涉及家庭群組。衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君稱，葵涌貨櫃碼頭多了3宗確診個案，其中一間公司，宏記港務操作有限公司至少錄8宗個案，5宗初步陽性個案。該公司約有120名員工，或需全送檢疫中心。<br />\n<br />\n張竹君稱，該公司設有一層休息室，內有沖涼室、碌架床、廁所及飯枱等，入面有員工過夜，或是傳播鏈之一。她又稱，相關工作地方會要求停工，清潔消毒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2725568/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E8%91%B5%E6%B6%8C%E8%B2%A8%E6%AB%83%E7%A2%BC%E9%A0%AD%E5%86%8D%E6%9C%89%E7%BE%A4%E7%B5%84%E7%88%86%E7%99%BC%E3%80%80%E5%AE%8F%E8%A8%98%E6%B8%AF%E5%8B%998%E5%AE%97%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E6%96%99%E7%99%BE%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E9%9C%80%E6%AA%A2%E7%96%AB?mtc=10012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2725568%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%2591%25B5%25E6%25B6%258C%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E6%25AB%2583%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%2599%25BC%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%25AE%258F%25E8%25A8%2598%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258B%25998%25E5%25AE%2597%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E6%2596%2599%25E7%2599%25BE%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E9%259C%2580%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E7%2596%25AB%3Fmtc%3D10012&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8QWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=a11e2e6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2725568/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E8%91%B5%E6%B6%8C%E8%B2%A8%E6%AB%83%E7%A2%BC%E9%A0%AD%E5%86%8D%E6%9C%89%E7%BE%A4%E7%B5%84%E7%88%86%E7%99%BC%E3%80%80%E5%AE%8F%E8%A8%98%E6%B8%AF%E5%8B%998%E5%AE%97%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E6%96%99%E7%99%BE%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E9%9C%80%E6%AA%A2%E7%96%AB?